{"tid":2048647,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【仲未完...】末日博士「貼中」美國暴動！之後全球股市冧40%？","createTime":"2020-06-03T02:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T04:01:42.000Z","uid":66087,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f5fc7662240d2cb5562a47a444250454337767a8","tid":2048647,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XG6ZGo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XG6ZGo.jpg&h=d5a5c5a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020-06-03 08:20<br />\n<br />\n外國媒體報道，曾準確預測2008年金融海嘯而獲「末日博士」稱號的紐約大學經濟學家魯比尼(Nouriel Roubini) 再度「貼中」，今次是「美國暴動」！<br />\n<br />\n事緣5月25日美國明尼蘇達州的非裔公民遭到白人警方以暴力執法致死，引發美國多州暴動示威。就此，魯比尼表示，他早在多月前已預測了美國將發生暴動。<br />\n<br />\n他在3月的一篇專欄文章中寫道，美國會出現徹底暴力和社會混亂的可能性，預測將會發生內亂。他指出，美國各地暴動不僅是非裔公民被警暴，現在美國失業人口達4,000萬，他們有足夠憤怒的理由，正如我幾個月前的預測，危機將導致騷亂和暴力。<br />\n<br />\n既然能準確預測暴動，那麼，之後如何呢？魯比尼建議，投資者要持有大量現金，<strong>因為他預計到今年底「全球」股市將大跌40%，2020年後全球經濟恐陷入「大蕭條」。</strong>"},{"pid":"8aa393d3d8d570701dd64fb450d1c43fb5554cda","tid":2048647,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"外媒 source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/the-economist-whos-warning-of-a-40-drop-in-the-stock-market-this-year-just-took-credit-for-predicting-the-riots-2020-06-01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketwatch.com%2Fstory%2Fthe-economist-whos-warning-of-a-40-drop-in-the-stock-market-this-year-just-took-credit-for-predicting-the-riots-2020-06-01&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgS6Ol0HYJA13lVA%2BPgi6hPY%3D&h=a349bcf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.marketwatch.com/story/the-economist-whos-warning-of-a-40-drop-in-the-stock-market-this-year-just-took-credit-for-predicting-the-riots-2020-06-01</a>"},{"pid":"2059242a56ed30dc69289161c5a84f5eb8ae261f","tid":2048647,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"跌40%咁撚少<img src=\"/asset